1960;;The House in Marsh Road;;British;;Montgomery Tully;;Tony Wright, Patricia Dainton;;thriller;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_House_in_Marsh_Road;;A spirit ("Patrick") haunts a house on a lonely country road. The house is inherited by Jean Linton, whose husband, David, is an unreliable heavy-drinking would-be author. Believing the house to be valuable and wishing to inherit, David plans with local sexpot Mrs Stockley to dispose of Jean. But "Patrick" has other ideas......